# QUICK REFERENCE FOR AI ASSISTANTS

## Build Decision in 5 Seconds

Ask yourself these questions in order:

1. **Did I change Dockerfile?** â†’ YES = Full rebuild (3-4 min) | NO = Continue â†“
2. **Did I change requirements.txt?** â†’ YES = Partial rebuild (2-3 min) | NO = Continue â†“
3. **Did I only change .py files?** â†’ YES = Fast build (~1 min) | NO = Check guide

